{
  "stem": "19921.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 98.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was named after a big Polish hero which really fought here in the Revolutionary War in the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other army, which was organized, which I first registered, was Sokorski.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was the general, and he was the head of the government of the Polish government in London.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, it was organized by people, by one of the-- at that time, he was a colonel, and his name was Zygmunt Berling.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Berling was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was the Chief of Staff of the General Anders, which he was in charge of the Polish army which went out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was his chief of staff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he decided to stay behind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, the closest way to Poland is not through the Western front but through the Eastern front.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The way he saw it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was not a Communist or any political leader.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was just brave soldier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, both of those gentlemen which would come out later in the story, both of them, Anders and Berling, with 300, 398 other people, high offices, were in the Katyn forest, if you're familiar with Katyn forest.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That will come out later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Where both of them in the same boat, and they were taking out-- those 400 officers were taking out by the Russians before anything started.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Even with the First-- with the First Army, they had something in plan so they took out 400 of those people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the rest, we know there what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they both were in Katyn forest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Survived.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was a colonel, a professional soldier during the, you know, in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, in the First World War and in the second.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In the first World War, he was with Pilsudski.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One promise.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
